    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chairs of various form designed to be used in a seaside recreational context. These are often designed to be lightweight, incorporating fabric or wicker, and may have the ability to be broken down and carried.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
